|z_{obs}|\le z_{1-\alpha/2} & \Leftrightarrow & |\bar{x}-\mu_{0}|\le z_{1-\alpha/2}\frac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n}}\\
 & \Leftrightarrow & \bar{x}-z_{1-\alpha/2}\frac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n}}\le\mu_{0}\le\bar{x}+z_{1-\alpha/2}\frac{\sigma}{\sqrt{n}}
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

 This implies that 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{0}$
\end_inset

 is in the 
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\alpha)100\%$
\end_inset

 confidence interval.
